    <div class="main review-item" id="4886509">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4886509/" class="title-link">很好的版本</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4886509"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/HugeEgoSorry/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3702256-5.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/HugeEgoSorry/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">Joyce</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-03-31"
      class="main-meta">2011-03-31 19:42:57</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4886509_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  上海古籍出版社的版本自然不错。 书价便宜，纸张较轻但不薄，有点点过去那种木浆纸的感觉。 不同颜色和字体排版，区分正文、注释、译文。虽然字体有些小。 我看完一遍，只发现了一个错字。  注释简要明白，译文灵活易懂。 每一篇前面有作者及文章背景介绍，有利于更好地理解文...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/4886509/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">5有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
